3.plot: George takes on a new challenge as he styles Tony Award winner Shuler Hensley and family for his opening in Waiting for Godot and No Man's Land.

4.title: Marin Mazzie

episode of.title: Dress Up! With George B. Style (TV Series 2014– )

4.plot: George styles the three-time Tony Award nominated actress Marin Mazzie for the opening night celebration of Bullets Over Broadway at the Metropolitan Museum of Art. They discuss style, clothing, and jewelry.

episode of.title: Dress Up! With George B. Style (TV Series 2014– )

5.plot: West End ingénue Alexandra Silber gets the Dress Up. treatment from George for the opening of the one-woman musical Arlington at the Vineyard Theatre.

6.title: Dress Up!: Jefferson Mays & Bryce Pinkham

episode of.title: Dress Up! With George B. Style (TV Series 2014– )

6.plot: Jefferson Mays and Bryce Pinkham, Tony nominees for A Gentleman's Guide to Love and Murder, meet up with stylist George Brescia at bespoke men's shop, Against Nature.

imdb.plot outline: As George likes to say, "When you feel amazing, you look amazing." Now you too can pick up some tips from "the master of fashion and personal well-being that is George Brescia." Join some of Broadway's most radiant stars as they prepare for glamorous galas and ritzy red carpets, all under the guidance of George's expert fashion advice that is heartfelt, entertaining, and always en vogue.
